<HEADLINE>
FT  10 DEC 94 / Weekend Money (Financial Planning): Top annuity rates
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An annuity provides a guaranteed income for life in return for a lump
sum investment. The bulk of the fund built up by many types of pension
plan must be used in this way. Annuity income is fully taxable. This
week's table shows the best rates for PERSONAL PENSION ANNUITIES which
are used for personal pension plans and the previous retirement annuity
contracts. The rates in the chart do not include inflation proofing.
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Male age 55     Annuity            Female age 50    Annuity (-0.01%)*
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
RNPFN           Pounds 7,696.20    Norwich Union     Pounds 6,841.56
Sun Life        Pounds 7,539.24    Sun Life          Pounds 6,827.76
Standard Life   Pounds 7,500.96    RNPFN             Pounds 6,806.40
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Male age 60     Annuity (%)        Female age 60     Annuity (%)
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
RNPFN           Pounds 8,456.40    RNPFN             Pounds 7,716.84
Standard Life   Pounds 8,182.68    Sun Life          Pounds 7,516.44
Sun Life        Pounds 8,158.32    Norwich Union     Pounds 7,495.56
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Male age 70     Annuity (%)        Female age 70     Annuity (%)
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
RNPFN           Pounds 11,154.12   RNPFN             Pounds 9,666.24
Sun Life        Pounds 10,429.20   Sun Life          Pounds 9,083.88
Standard Life   Pounds 10,380.24   Norwich Union     Pounds 8,999.28
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
